%F A366457 G.f.: (59*x^2 - 115*x + 58)/(1 - x)^3.
%F A366457 a(n) = 3*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2) + a(n-3) with a(0) = 58, a(1) = 59 and a(2) = 62.
%F A366457 Sum_{n>=0} 1/a(n) = (1+sqrt(58)*Pi*coth(sqrt(58)*Pi))/116 = 0.2148763... - _R. J. Mathar_, Apr 24 2024
